&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-uuid=&quot;77c7d14a-bce4-43f3-b396-05f2c872059d&quot;&gt;5+ years of professional UI Art experience in game development, with at least one shipped AAA title&lt;/li&gt;
